Usage: setSelectedDensityArea [-help] <x1> <y1> <x2> <y2> <density> <name>
                              [{Partial Soft Hard}]
                              [{Instance Pushdown Undefined}]

-help                             # Prints out the command usage
<x1>                              # X1 (float, required)
<y1>                              # Y1 (float, required)
<x2>                              # X2 (float, required)
<y2>                              # Y2 (float, required)
<density>                         # Standard cell placement density percentage
                                  # (float, required, min=0, max=100)
<name>                            # Name of the density screen area
                                  # (string, required)
{Partial Soft Hard}               # hardness of the density screen area
                                  # (enum, optional)
{Instance Pushdown Undefined}     # relationship of the density screen area to
                                  # the design (enum, optional)